Application.Domain

Class ReferralCodeScenario

  • java.lang.Object
    • Application.Domain.ReferralCodeScenario

  • @Entity
public class ReferralCodeScenario
extends java.lang.Object
    ReferralCodeScenario is the class that maps the database Entity ReferralCodeScenario. A ReferralCodeScenario is the mapping class between ReferralCode and Scenario.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Corti Lorenzo, Tocchetti Andrea
